interface

{$i IdCompilerDefines.inc}

{
 Indy HTTP proxy Server

 Original Programmer: Bas Gooijen (bas_gooijen@yahoo.com)
 Current Maintainer:  Bas Gooijen
   Code is given to the Indy Pit Crew.

